{"tid":1373619,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[不分化不責備] 理性討論如何撤退","createTime":"2019-07-27T15:54:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T02:59:06.000Z","uid":190579,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"88c618e4ef06b2f49d5d87f67c6fabb10de43e87","tid":1373619,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:54:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">撤退係必要的</span>，最多頂到凌晨1點都要撤退。<br />\n<br />\n1) 前線騰出一兩個人做咪手，負責去中後排收風同止謡，<br />\n前線要留番一兩個咪手既朋友負責聯絡<br />\n<br />\n2) 中後排<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好人云亦云</span></strong>，聽完可以信住先，但唔好傳<br />\n防止一個大話被唔同人講一千次變咗真話<br />\n<br />\n3) 撤退要一個鐘通知，少於一個鐘概不受理 (如非緊急)<br />\n<br />\n4) <span style=\"color: red;\">未建立好人鏈就唔退</span> (如非緊急)<br />\n<br />\n<ins>撤退秩序：</ins><br />\n<br />\n預訂時間30分鐘前：<br />\n咪手帶領後排同最前線建立人鏈，人人搭住前面膊頭 (如果咪手齋叫人散，又唔幫手組人鏈，就知咩料)<br />\n<br />\n到達預訂時間：<br />\n準時由最前排開始，面向警犬背向後排後退。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">未建立好人鏈就唔退</span></span>"},{"pid":"61cb932e87b98c7ccde288ce76f6a0277c99fb88","tid":1373619,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:54:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"20c45bcf529fe44da2d918ed64c9fbcc1ab4f16c","tid":1373619,"uid":208452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:54:43.000Z","msg":"PUSH<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">希望大家入去填低感受</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">已經收左集超過二百人嘅感受，幫我地推到上一千、二千 OK ？</span></span><br />\n出一本屬於香港人嘅自由之書<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1359361\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1359361</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f9034ab4b835aa59ecdb64feb2cad1a303ee26a0","tid":1373619,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3f18570dfbac77b9cb14f65b258e5c347d912ac8","tid":1373619,"uid":190579,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cite